<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">“生活不是我们活过的日子，而是我们记住的日子，我们为了讲述而在记忆中重现的日子。”</span></p>
<p><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>复工记 | </span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span><span>“没有想过转行，有希望总是好事”</span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span></span><span></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 16px;">坚持总比放弃来得容易。</span></p>